name: Portal
description:
Access to other spheres of consciousness..
Times dilating the experience of being pulse and pause..

Breathing with time
until part of the lucid 
link of shapes 
bend the concrete
break down 
substance into ethereal fluid..


At departure from the times of remain...

Edited photo of cemetery gate.(Brasil-2021)
